# Custom Parameters
Custom parameters are a way to add custom fields to your users.

They are very flexible and you can add different types of parameters to individual user instances.

Additionally you can add a custom param config. this config is used during the signup process to define the fields that should be shown to the user.
Custom params can be used without a custom param config. For an example on how to use this see the [Create user](#create-user) endpoint.    




