## Create custom params config

> Request example

```typescript
const user = await client.tenant('624c14cc0c01e70033356285').users.create(
    {
        "params": [
          {
      
            "label": "department",  
            "userLabel":"Department",    
            "type":"text"
          },
          {
            "label": "employeeId",      
            "userLabel":"Employee ID",    
            "type":"text"
          },
            {
            "label": "additionalmail",      
            "userLabel":"additionalmail",    
            "type":"email"
          }
        ]
    }

```

```shell
curl --request POST '<%= config[:account_api_url] %>/app/custom-tenant-user-params-config' \
--header 'x-api-key: <%= config[:api_key] %>' \
--header 'x-tenant-id: 624c14cc0c01e70033356285' \
--header 'Content-Type: application/json' \
--data-raw '{"params":[{"label":"department","userLabel":"Department","type":"text"},{"label":"employeeId","userLabel":"Employee ID","type":"text"},{"label":"additionalmail","userLabel":"additionalmail","type":"email"}]}'
```

